  {
    "type": "hardware-ref",
    "page": "hardware-reference",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "entries": [
      {
        "src": "fastener_11_SHCS_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Socket head cap screw (SHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角圆柱头螺钉（SHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Cylindrical head, hex drive.",
          "zh": "圆柱头，用内六角扳手拧。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912",
          "zh": "ISO 4762 / DIN 912"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_10_BHCS_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Button head cap screw (BHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角半圆头螺钉（BHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Domed head, hex drive. Used on surfaces where a lower profile matters but a flush head isn't required.",
          "zh": "圆顶头，用内六角扳手拧。用在既想压低高度、又不必和表面齐平的地方。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 7380-1",
          "zh": "ISO 7380-1"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_12_FHCS_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Flat head cap screw (FHCS)",
          "zh": "内六角沉头螺钉（FHCS）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "90° countersunk head, hex drive. Sits flush with the surface — used where nothing can protrude above the part.",
          "zh": "90° 沉头，用内六角扳手拧。和表面齐平，用在不能高出零件表面的地方。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 10642 / DIN 7991",
          "zh": "ISO 10642 / DIN 7991"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_40_shim_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Shim",
          "zh": "垫片"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "5×8×0.5 shim. Stacked under each idler to set its axial play — measure yours, thickness varies by supplier.",
          "zh": "5×8×0.5 垫片。叠在每个惰轮下面，决定它的轴向间隙——不同供应商厚度不同，记得先量一下。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "5×8×0.5",
          "zh": "5×8×0.5"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_21_hex_nut_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Hex nut",
          "zh": "六角螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Pairs with a bolt to clamp parts firmly together.",
          "zh": "和螺栓配合，把零件牢牢夹紧。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934",
          "zh": "ISO 4032 / DIN 934"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_20_square_nut_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Square nut",
          "zh": "四方螺母"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "A square nut sits in a pocket of the printed part so it can't spin, letting you tighten a bolt into it.",
          "zh": "四方螺母嵌进打印件的方槽里不会转动，配上螺栓就能拧紧固定。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "DIN 557",
          "zh": "DIN 557"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "hardware-ref",
    "page": "hardware-reference-2",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — REFERENCE",
        "zh": "五金件 — 参考"
      }
    },
    "entries": [
      {
        "src": "fastener_22_tnut_standard_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Standard T-nut (slide-in)",
          "zh": "滑块 T 型螺母（端部滑入）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Slides into the slot from the open end of the extrusion. As you tighten the screw, the nut is pulled up and catches on the inner edges of the slot opening.",
          "zh": "从型材的开口端滑进滑槽。拧紧螺钉时，螺母被往上拉，卡住滑槽开口的内侧边缘。"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_23_tnut_hammer_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Hammer T-nut (drop-in)",
          "zh": "船形 T 型螺母（任意位置放入）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Drops flat into a slot anywhere along its length, then a quarter turn locks it — no need to reach an open end.",
          "zh": "可以从滑槽的任意位置平放进去，转 90° 就卡紧，不必从型材开口端穿进来。"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_30_pulley_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 drive pulley",
          "zh": "GT2 同步带轮"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "20-tooth toothed pulley. One sits on each stepper shaft, locked to the motor's D-flat with a set screw; it drives the GT2 belt.",
          "zh": "20 齿同步带轮。每个步进电机轴上装一个，用顶丝顶在电机的 D 形扁位上，由它带动 GT2 同步带。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "GT2 · 20T · 5 mm bore · 6 mm belt",
          "zh": "GT2 · 20 齿 · 孔径 5 mm · 带宽 6 mm"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_31_idler_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 idler (toothed)",
          "zh": "GT2 惰轮（带齿）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Free-spinning wheel that turns the belt around the frame corners.",
          "zh": "自由转动的轮子，在框架拐角处给同步带转向。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "GT2 · 20T · 5 mm bore · 6 mm belt",
          "zh": "GT2 · 20 齿 · 孔径 5 mm · 带宽 6 mm"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_32_idler_smooth_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "GT2 idler (smooth)",
          "zh": "GT2 惰轮（光面）"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Un-toothed turn wheel for the belt's flat back.",
          "zh": "无齿的转向轮，贴着同步带的平背面转。"
        },
        "ref": {
          "en": "5 mm bore · 6 mm belt",
          "zh": "孔径 5 mm · 带宽 6 mm"
        }
      },
      {
        "src": "fastener_41_flat_bracket_assembled_cam1.svg",
        "h3": {
          "en": "Flat bracket",
          "zh": "一字连接板"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "Two-hole plate with M5 holes 20 mm apart.",
          "zh": "两孔平板，M5 孔间距 20 mm。"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "tall-left",
    "page": "hardware-reference-3",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "HARDWARE — TOOLS",
        "zh": "五金件 — 工具"
      }
    },
    "figures": [
      {
        "src": "fastener_50_hex_driver_assembled_cam1.svg"
      }
    ],
    "notes": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "2 mm & 3 mm hex drivers",
          "zh": "2 mm 和 3 mm 内六角扳手"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "The 2 mm and 3 mm hex drivers see the most use in this build. A quality driver for each is strongly recommended. Refer to the sourcing guide for suggestions.",
          "zh": "装配这台机器时，2 mm 和 3 mm 内六角扳手用得最多。强烈建议这两把扳手都用质量好的。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:152mm; top:56mm; width:120mm;"
      },
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Driver sizes",
          "zh": "扳手规格"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "These cover the socket screws used in this build — 2 mm for M3 button/flat head screws, 3 mm for M5 button/flat head screws (BHCS/FHCS), and 5 mm for M6 socket head cap screws (SHCS).",
          "zh": "这几把扳手覆盖本次装配用到的内六角螺钉——2 mm 对应 M3 半圆头/沉头螺钉，3 mm 对应 M5 半圆头/沉头螺钉，5 mm 对应 M6 内六角圆柱头螺钉。"
        },
        "classes": "note overlay sm",
        "style": "left:152mm; top:108mm; width:120mm;"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "type": "printed-parts",
    "page": "printed-parts",
    "head": {
      "title": {
        "en": "3D PRINTED PARTS",
        "zh": "3D 打印件"
      }
    },
    "notesBefore": [
      {
        "h3": {
          "en": "Part printing settings and guidelines",
          "zh": "零件打印设置与说明"
        },
        "body": {
          "en": "PhysiClaw's custom parts are printed by Selective Laser Sintering (SLS), not the common FDM. A laser fuses nylon powder in a heated powder bed, so parts come out fully solid, support-free, and strong in every direction. These parts carry side holes and overhangs: with FDM the side holes deform and the overhangs sag. Match the specifications below when sourcing parts.",
          "zh": "PhysiClaw 的定制零件用选择性激光烧结（SLS）打印，而不是常见的 FDM。激光在加热的粉末床里把尼龙粉末烧结成型，做出来的零件完全实心、不用支撑，各个方向都很结实。这些零件带有侧面的孔和悬空结构，用 FDM 打，侧孔会变形、悬空处会塌陷。采购零件时，请对照下面的规格。"
        },
        "classes": "note"
      }
    ],
    "specs": [
      {
